data.description: Welcome to your next home sweet home.  Head around back to the private covered porch.  Large great room with a gas fireplace is ready for cozy winter evenings.  Sparkling granite countertops, center island, stainless appliances, double oven and a walk in pantry make up the kitchen you've been dreaming of with a breakfast room for family meals.  Large separate dining room for formal gathering during holidays and any special occasions.  Large main floor laundry room.  Large three bedrooms and a master bedroom with a luxury bath with separate jetted tub, dual sink vanity and two walk in closets.  The basement is a blank slate ready to be finished with a rough in for a bath and an egress window.
